Package: weaiR
Title: Women's Empowerment in Agriculture Index (WEAI)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("WEAI Team", email = "weai@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes the Women's Empowerment in Agriculture Index (WEAI) family
    of indices, including WEAI, A-WEAI, and pro-WEAI from pre-computed binary
    adequacy indicators. Implements the Alkire-Foster methodology for measuring
    empowerment, including the Five/Three Domains of Empowerment (5DE/3DE)
    sub-index, Gender Parity Index (GPI), and indicator-level decomposition.
    Supports survey designs via the 'survey' package and subgroup decomposition.
